; Regression test for issue #1126: ledger xact uses --date-format instead of --input-date-format (BZ#1126)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1126
;
; The bug: when --input-date-format is set to a non-default format (e.g. European dd/mm/yyyy),
; the xact command should use --input-date-format to parse the date argument on the command line.
; Previously, xact was using --date-format for parsing instead of --input-date-format.

2014/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test --input-date-format '%d/%m/%Y' xact 01/02/2014 Groceries
2014/02/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food                            $100.00
    Assets:Checking
end test
